               boolean isTrending)
        This is the preferred constructor implementation as it forces us to specify all of the values that are not nullable
        Parameters:
        productName - This is a String for the name of the product
        stockLevel - This is the number of stock that is currently being held for this product
        minimumThreshold - This is the minimum level of stock that can be held before more stock needs to be ordered
        recommendedLevel - This is the level of stock that will be ordered to when stock reaches the minimum threshold
        isPorousware - This indicates whether this item should be treated for porousware
        price - This is the price of the product
